OL,3,CHolidaymakers 'trimming budgets this
OL,4,Csummer amid cost-of-living concerns'
OL,6,FHolidaymakers are trimming their
OL,7,Fbudgets this summer and looking for
OL,8,Fways to make their money stretch
OL,9,Ffurther amid economic and political
OL,10,Funcertainty and worries about rising
OL,11,Fliving costs, research suggests.
OL,13,FFour-fifths (83%) of people aim to cut
OL,14,Fback on their travel spending this
OL,15,Fsummer, research for home-swapping
OL,16,Fplatform Kindred found.
OL,18,FOne in eight (12%) said they have
OL,19,Fmanaged to cut some of their holiday
OL,20,Fcosts so far.
