OL,3,CHolidaymakers 'trimming budgets this
OL,4,Csummer amid cost-of-living concerns'
OL,6,FAmong those who have saved money, a
OL,7,Ffifth (22%) were worried about ongoing
OL,8,Fpolitical or economic uncertainty, two-
OL,9,Ffifths (40%) were concerned about the
OL,10,Fincreased cost of living, a third
OL,11,F(36%) were worried about rising travel
OL,12,Fcosts and three in 10 (30%) were
OL,13,Fmotivated to save on holidays by
OL,14,Fhaving less disposable income.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, one in seven (14%) said
OL,17,Fthey would be willing to skip going on
OL,18,Fholiday altogether.
