OL,3,CHolidaymakers 'trimming budgets this
OL,4,Csummer amid cost-of-living concerns'
OL,6,FNearly four in 10 (39%) are looking
OL,7,Ffor more cost-effective accommodation
OL,8,Fwhile others are staying with friends
OL,9,For family (30%) and just over a
OL,10,Fquarter (26%) are opting for
OL,11,Fstaycations.
OL,13,FThe research also found that
OL,14,Ffrustrations with hotels expressed by
OL,15,Fsome holidaymakers included the cost
OL,16,Fof "extras", unreliable wifi and the
OL,17,Fcost of dining.
