OL,3,CHolidaymakers 'trimming budgets this
OL,4,Csummer amid cost-of-living concerns'
OL,6,FNearly six in 10 (59%) people said
OL,7,Fthey are making changes to how they
OL,8,Ftravel this summer, according to the
OL,9,Fsurvey carried out by OnePoll among
OL,10,F2,000 people across the UK in April
OL,11,Fand May.
OL,13,FMore than a quarter (27%) are seeking
OL,14,Fmore cost-effective trips, 16% are
OL,15,Flooking for "ways to live like a
OL,16,Flocal", and 16% are aiming to travel
OL,17,Fin a sustainable way. One in six (15%)
OL,18,Fare looking to make more frequent
OL,19,Ftrips by using affordable
OL,20,Faccommodation options.
