OL,3,CHolidaymakers 'trimming budgets this
OL,4,Csummer amid cost-of-living concerns'
OL,6,FJustine Palefsky, CEO and co-founder
OL,7,Fat Kindred, said: "We're seeing a
OL,8,Fclear shift toward more thoughtful,
OL,9,Fvalue-driven travel that aligns with
OL,10,Fboth budget and beliefs.
OL,12,F"Travellers still want to explore the
OL,13,Fworld but they're seeking options that
OL,14,Foffer greater connection, flexibility
OL,15,Fand authenticity."
